<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Log&nbsp;2015/09/17</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Log&nbsp;2015/09/17</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/what-dragons-we-shall-be/TriBanner.png" alt="TriBanner.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Fang! I see that you're finally catching up with the trend!</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>well hello to you too Tri<br />
and yeah, boss order. sayin that it's easier and safer to work with.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I can see that your boss is a very wise person.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>it's just weird to put an AI in your phone? seems like the opposite of safe to me</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Hey, AIs have rights and feelings too, several of my respected colleagues are AIs. :(</p>
<p>Nah I'm just kidding. This is not even a proper AI, more like a fragment, probably responds to the main thing back in AR headquarters. It's just here to help secure communications and manage your things. So I wouldn't worry about that.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>heh, you're the expert. computers I'm good at are something else entirely<br />
still, why is it called Reunion anyways, seems kinda strange</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>A kind of falcon, Réunion kestrel I think. The Anderson people are obessessed with those, for some reason.</p>
<p>I mean it's actually extinct, so who knows what they're thinking. They probably just scribbled the logo in MS Paint.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>uh sure<br />
why are you so formal tho, all of a sudden?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Um?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I mean, proper capitalization and punctuations, you don't even shorten the words.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>OH. I see.</p>
<p>That's a beauty of this app, Fang. I can directly access this through my implant! I'm not even really typing right now, it's very helpful.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>wait, so you're just thinking this conversation up? and making no mistakes?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Hey, I'm an OP, don't question my professionality. It's what I do all day.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>&#8230;sorry?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>It's cool. Although you've got to hang out here more, there's more to it than just chatting.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>yeah I've heard that it's like an anomalous version of facebook</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Oh it's more then that. But essentially, yeah, ideal place to get in touch with people in this circle.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>and do anomalous posting</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Yep! Pretty sure those benders are setting up a group here. Saw some art too.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>ugh reality benders</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Is there anything wrong? &#8230;Something happened?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>no just, that brings me back to my research again<br />
and it's just, stagnation</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>You can rant to me if you want to.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>ugh I dunno<br />
you know what I've been working on right?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Yeah.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>it just<br />
makes<br />
no<br />
goddamn<br />
sense</p>
<p>I've been looking up stuff all over the place, I went through all our old documents, asked around your church, visited magicians, even managed to get people to look up things in the Library for me<br />
I guess I still need to try anartists but there's just all this conflicting stuff and they're all correct<br />
I dunno what to do feels like it's all useless</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Well, we all know that our world is more than a little chaotic.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>no I mean like how are there are so many kinds of magic and all those different systems and theories, beyond that there's also the measurement of the reality's stablility, and the boaders between reality bending and magic and anomalies</p>
<p>ugh sorry I'm just babbling right now<br />
I'm such a mess</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I've heard that people's perception will affect how things work? How a lot of gods are shaped by people's faith. Maybe it's something similar?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>that<br />
that part makes even less sense</p>
<p>how can our mere thoughts affect those<br />
and if it universally applies, which it may actually does according to my research<br />
is there a universal law indicating that how gods are created and how things are affected by thoughts<br />
but there's no clear common law between systems<br />
and where does the ordinary laws of physics end and where does the magic stuff begin?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>It's okay Fang. This a big topic, and it's bound to be difficult.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>yeah but<br />
I'm just furstrated</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Don't stress yourself out. It will work out.</p>
<p>Actually, why not read a story? I just happen to have an interesting one and it will help you relax.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>um okay I guess</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="text-align: right; margin: auto; width: 300px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 10pt; background:#000000; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><a href="/the-maker-and-the-beast">The Maker and the Beast</a>.txt</p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Here.</p>
<p>Who knows, maybe it will even help provide some insprations. :P</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>haha thanks, but no way</p>
<p>what is it about, anyways</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>How about you take a read first?</p>
<p>The one true god, WAN, and the flesh god, of course. :3</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>yes, yes, WAN, our fave god<br />
I'll see when I can get to it then</p>
<p>I should get to things now</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#FFED97;; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Cool! See you then.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Log&nbsp;2015/09/18</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Log&nbsp;2015/09/18</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/what-dragons-we-shall-be/GuBanner.png" alt="GuBanner.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Dale.<br />
Finally setting the app up?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Yes, Mr. Gu. It is pretty convenient.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Good. It is time you take some initiative and get more informed about this circle. Gotta stop burying youself with work.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Sorry, I was just really caught up in it.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>You know you don't have to stress yourself, we aren't exactly a profit oriented group.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I understand, sir.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Came across anything interesting on the site?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Yes, actually, I've been meaning to ask, have you heard about the &quot;Maker and Beast&quot; story of the two dragons?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Ah, the Fuxi establishing the laws of physics to protect us against the gods of Guixu? Yeah, we do have a few versions of that floating around.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I would like to take a look, sir. It may help me with my reseach.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Back to the research again, huh?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
