<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I'm just really busy with my research stuff<br />
I met with a few anartists, and that's most of the stuff done, I'm really piecing this together here<br />
I don't think I really have time now, or any time soon</p>
<p>how about we fix some other time?</p>
</div>
