<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Log&nbsp;2016/07/19</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Log&nbsp;2015/07/19</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="image-container alignleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/what-dragons-we-shall-be/GuBanner.png" alt="GuBanner.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Mr. Gu?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Yes, Dale?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Have you read through the reports and proposals I sent you?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Yes, and I have to say, those are some very interesting ideas.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I know, right?</p>
<p>I think this is it. Everything comes together, this explains how the gods are affected by faith, how differet magic systems works, and how reality benders come to be.<br />
Tech, magic, reality bending, they can all be unified under this theory. All I need is to set up bigger experiments and figure out how to make use of this.</p>
<p>We will have the chance to utilize the laws of our world way better. And it would really be something if we can properly seperate and refine the aspects of the two dragons within us.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>That's all very good Dale. But about your proposals, I'm afraid that I cannot grant them.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>But, Mr. Gu.<br />
Is this about the money? I can certainly start small and I can pull some of my current funding into this, it won't be that costly, and I promise there will be results, actual results we can use really soon.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I understand that, and I do believe you. But that is not the problem.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Then what is it? I'll do whatever I can to fix it!</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>We're running out of time. The crack on Taisui is widening.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>That's the reason? It would take decades and centuries before something even happens!</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>You don't know that, Dale. We don't know that.</p>
<p>And even if we have the chance to mend it, it will only stall time before Nüwa breaks free and Fuxi regains his form. And we cannot survive through another war of the dragons.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>We don't even know what would happen if they're freed! And you're denying my research for this?</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Sorry, but the decision has been made. There will be no more additional funding and no more new projects. All resources are now relocated to the evacuation plan, and frankly, we only need more.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>How can you do this to me? You've seen my papers, you know what it's worth!</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I know. But it will no longer matter once we leave. The rules of the world will be different.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>But we'll still be the same! We can still work on that, and it will still help!</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I understand your frustration, but we won't be able to get to it currently.</p>
<p>You can always go through the transformation and prolong your life. When we settle again, you'll have the chance to carry on your research.<br />
Your father is already working on the site, and you should be there too.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Back again at convincing me to turn into &quot;dragons&quot; you so desire? I thought we were just now trying to run away from the dragons!</p>
<p>And my father, yes, I guess he's the perfect example you really want.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Dale, that's not what I meant.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>No, Mr. Gu, I'm not even going.<br />
The hell with your bullshit.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#BEBEBE; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>Dale.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 500px; text-align: right;">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; background:#A6FFA6; text-align: left; padding: 1px 20px;">
<p>I thought you were different from them, I thought you treated me good, but no, you're the same.</p>
<p>Goodbye.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br /></div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
