<blockquote>
<p><strong>Event Description:</strong> At 3 P.M. local time, 167 individuals reported experiencing a sudden &quot;awareness&quot; of a great web surrounding them as they passed by the residence of one Dale Fang. Witnesses described sensing a giant snake emerging from the residence, flying up along the web's lines. Accounts conflict, but the web was typically described as metallic, while the snake was described as &quot;mechanical&quot;.</p>
